<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id6c275192-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e" identifier="/us/usc/t33/s1976"><num value="1976">§ 1976.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Of the amounts authorized under <ref href="/us/usc/t33/s1968/a">section 1968(a) of this title</ref>, the Secretary of Commerce shall use up to $1,000,000 to carry out this subchapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id6c275193-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e">(<ref href="/us/pl/109/449/s126">Pub. L. 109–449, § 126</ref>, formerly <ref href="/us/pl/116/224/tI/s126">Pub. L. 116–224, title I, § 126</ref>, <date date="2020-12-18">Dec. 18, 2020</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/134/1083">134 Stat. 1083</ref>; renumbered <ref href="/us/pl/109/449/s126">Pub. L. 109–449, § 126</ref>, by <ref href="/us/pl/119/65/s4/a">Pub. L. 119–65, § 4(a)</ref>, <date date="2025-12-26">Dec. 26, 2025</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/139/1989">139 Stat. 1989</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
